OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sun 7 Jun to Sun 21 JunFThe
OL,6,Fweather may be a little unsettled
OL,7,Finitially, with drier weather expected
OL,8,Fbetween any bouts of wetter weather.
OL,9,FThese drier interludes will tend to
OL,10,Flast longer across the south and east
OL,11,Fof England and Wales. By mid June
OL,12,Fthere is slightly more evidence that
OL,13,Fhigh pressure will dominate, bringing
OL,14,Fmore in the way of dry weather for
OL,15,Fmuch of the time. However this does
OL,16,Fnot rule out showery intervals, which
OL,17,Fcan be heavy and thundery this time of
OL,18,Fyear. Temperatures are most likely to
OL,19,Fbe near or slightly above average
OL,20,Foverall, with some warm or very warm
OL,21,Fweather about.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
